  "detailed_description": "<h1>My first 3D game!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Art by Khud0</h2><br><strong>Important information</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Press \"N\" for night mode.<br></li><li>Press \"Del\" then \"Esc\" to reset all achievements.</li></ul><br>100 hidden aliens is a hidden object game in the cosmic setting.<br>Black and white hand-drawn graphics in a cartoon style.<br><br>Aliens come in very different shapes. <br>They are like everything. And they are not like everything. <br>Try to find them all. Don't be afraid of alien music.<br>This is a cute game for all ages.",
